Signed-off-by: Kuninori Morimoto <kuninori.morimoto.gx@renesas.com>
Link: https://lore.kernel.org/r/20250217215641.372723-4-detlev.casanova@collabora.com
Signed-off-by: Heiko Stuebner <heiko@sntech.de>

